        <mxCell id="assume" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#5A6B86;fontSize=10;" value="All data encrypted at rest (SSE-KMS) and in transit (TLS); access controlled via least-privilege IAM roles and Lake Formation permissions. Serverless Glue auto-scales (DPU); parquet + partitioning at every curated stage. Canonical S3 zones used identically across all diagrams: raw → cleansed → curated → sandbox, with a single quarantine sink." vertex="1">
